1. *Sunce* se krije za oblakom. (The sun is hiding behind a cloud.)
2. *Sunce* se dugo zadržalo iza oblaka. (The sun stayed behind the clouds for a long time.)
3. Uživali smo u toplom *suncu*. (We enjoyed the warm sun.)
4. *Suncem* osvetljena soba bila je puna svetlosti. (The room lit by the sun was full of light.)
5. Zalazeće *sunce* je prekrasno. (The setting sun is beautiful.)